rows.label: qst701917_msg0002
rows.name:
With this, Morumo grow one step
closer to atoning for sins.

rows.label: qst701917_msg0003
rows.name:
Morumo will definitely be useful
on expedition!

rows.label: qst701917_msg0102
rows.name:
We sure to get Dragon Incense
and come back safely!

rows.label: qst701917_msg0103
rows.name:
Friends probably dubious about mission
success, but please to not worry!

rows.label: qst701917_msg0201
rows.name:
This not nearly enough to pay for
crimes of Morumo, me know that.

rows.label: qst701917_msg0202
rows.name:
But still want to be of service to
community and continue with good
deeds, even if little.

rows.label: qst701917_msg0203
rows.name:
That Morumo's way of atonement,
and is how will be from now on.
